<font color='#7F7E6F'>&#62;&#62; major impact to the FTS operation and require that all Tier 0/Tier 1</font>
<font color='#7F7E6F'>&#62;&#62; site FTS servers to reconfigure their channels to BNL,   I would like</font>
<font color='#7F7E6F'>&#62;&#62; to do it after March when ATLAS will  do large scale productions.</font>
<font color='#7F7E6F'>&#62;&#62;</font>
<font color='#7F7E6F'>&#62;&#62; Even we do not expect any potential impact to the OSG/WLCG Grid</font>
<font color='#7F7E6F'>&#62;&#62; operation and monitoring, but anyway we would like to send out a</font>
<font color='#7F7E6F'>&#62;&#62; global announcement since it might potential affect OSG/WLCG</font>
<font color='#7F7E6F'>&#62;&#62; availability number publish and operations which are not directly</font>
<font color='#7F7E6F'>&#62;&#62; under BNL site control.</font>
<font color='#7F7E6F'>&#62;&#62;</font>
<font color='#7F7E6F'>&#62;&#62; Thank you very much,</font>
<font color='#7F7E6F'>&#62;&#62; Dantong</font>
