<font color='#7F7E6F'>&#62; tests.  The BNL storage element is not associated with BNL-LCG2 which</font>
<font color='#7F7E6F'>&#62; Alessandro is testing.  (We tried to accommodate OSG availability by removing</font>
<font color='#7F7E6F'>&#62; dcsrm from BNL-LCG2 and registering it into BNL_ATLAS_SE.).</font>
<font color='#7F7E6F'>&#62;</font>
